item.title: Ok
item.dc:creator: @Mod_Baker Mod Baker
item.description:
@Mod_Baker wrote:

Wow please neat this up a bit. I really dont know what youre saying.
Get No-Ip, then make a account, after that click “click here to sign in to No-IP and create hosts.” at the very bottom, and follow the form.
Click the host to update then run your Runserver. Try loggoing in, and if it doesnt work then you 43594 port is not open.
